node.title: Police launch homicide investigation after South Auckland death
node.description: A homicide investigation has been launched following the death of a man in the South Auckland suburb of Favona overnight.
node.content:
["A homicide investigation has been launched following the death of a man in the South Auckland suburb of Favona overnight.", "", "
\nPhoto: 123rf.com\n
", "Emergency services were called to the Abiru Crescent scene just before 4am.", "The man had critical injuries when staff arrived but died at the scene.", "In a statement, Police said they were speaking with someone in relation to the incident and a scene examination would start this morning."]
